{
  "__inputs": [
    {
      "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
      "label": "Prometheus-Lab",
      "description": "Selecciona Prometheus-Lab al importar",
      "type": "datasource",
      "pluginId": "prometheus",
      "pluginName": "Prometheus"
    }
  ],
  "__requires": [
    {
      "type": "grafana",
      "id": "grafana",
      "name": "Grafana",
      "version": "11.5.0"
    },
    {
      "type": "datasource",
      "id": "prometheus",
      "name": "Prometheus",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "table",
      "name": "Table",
      "version": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "timeseries",
      "name": "Time series",
      "version": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "id": "text",
      "name": "Text",
      "version": ""
    }
  ],
  "uid": "lab-m06-02-prom-join",
  "title": "Lab M06-02 — Mixed Prom merge/join",
  "tags": ["lab", "example", "m06", "mixed", "join"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": { "from": "now-6h", "to": "now" },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Mixed — RX + TX por device (merge + join + cálculo)",
      "description": "Datasource Mixed: query A y B en Prometheus. Pipeline: Merge → Join by device → Organize → Calculate Total.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "datasource", "uid": "-- Mixed --" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by (device) (rate(node_network_receive_bytes_total{job=\"node-exporter\", device!~\"lo|veth.*\"}[5m]))",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "__auto",
          "range": false,
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by (device) (rate(node_network_transmit_bytes_total{job=\"node-exporter\", device!~\"lo|veth.*\"}[5m]))",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "__auto",
          "range": false,
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "Bps",
          "decimals": 2
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "sortBy": [{ "desc": true, "displayName": "Total (B/s)" }]
      },
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "merge",
          "options": {}
        },
        {
          "id": "joinByField",
          "options": {
            "byField": "device",
            "mode": "outer"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": { "Time": true },
            "renameByName": {
              "device": "Interfaz",
              "Value #A": "RX (B/s)",
              "Value #B": "TX (B/s)"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "calculateField",
          "options": {
            "alias": "Total (B/s)",
            "binary": {
              "left": "RX (B/s)",
              "operator": "+",
              "reducer": "sum",
              "right": "TX (B/s)"
            },
            "mode": "binary",
            "reduce": { "reducer": "sum" }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Mixed — mismas queries A/B en time series (sin transform)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 10 },
      "datasource": { "type": "datasource", "uid": "-- Mixed --" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by (device) (rate(node_network_receive_bytes_total{job=\"node-exporter\", device!~\"lo|veth.*\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "RX {{device}}",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by (device) (rate(node_network_transmit_bytes_total{job=\"node-exporter\", device!~\"lo|veth.*\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "TX {{device}}",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "Bps",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true, "calcs": ["mean", "max"] },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Pipeline didáctico",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 18 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Lab M06-02 — Mixed solo Prometheus\n\n**Panel 1 (Table, datasource `-- Mixed --`):**\n\n1. **Query A** — RX por `device` (Instant + Table)\n2. **Query B** — TX por `device` (Instant + Table)\n3. **Merge** — apila resultados A y B\n4. **Join by field** — clave `device` (outer)\n5. **Organize fields** — renombra columnas\n6. **Add field from calculation** — `Total = RX + TX`\n\n**Panel 2** — mismas queries en **Range** (time series), sin transforms.\n\n> Si el join falla al importar, edita panel 1 → Transformations y confirma campo **`device`** en Join."
      }
    }
  ],
  "templating": { "list": [] }
}
